public static class ConfigTemplates.BiomeStructureConfig
extends ConfigTemplates.StructureConfig
    Extension of ConfigTemplates.StructureConfig that allows allows stores what biomes a structure should generate in. Use this setting in FMLCommonSetupEvent to register the structure in the appropriate biomes.
